{"tid":620933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"V-Bar比基尼強化乳溝線條　海灘超搶眼","createTime":"2018-04-08T00:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T05:16:01.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"60f18411f92c3c3938fb38cc1357b120ddfaaa7d","tid":620933,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T00:41:49.000Z","msg":"V-Bar會在女性胸口形成一個倒V，據說其中的鋼圈和這個倒V可以加強集中、托高的效果，營造更美麗的胸型。<br />\n<br />\n巴西名模Gizele Oliveira已經多次在IG秀出V-Bar比基尼。澳洲名模Shannon Lawson、Madi Edwards的也都在海邊換穿了V-Bar比基尼。知名部落客Kallie Kaiser在YouTub上試穿、發表心得評論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180408/640_39cd58f19d7a9b0a7622d36bd8f70d57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180408%2F640_39cd58f19d7a9b0a7622d36bd8f70d57.jpg&h=53cc48e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180408/640_1c8cc1d3bd340ead07583a330823998d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180408%2F640_1c8cc1d3bd340ead07583a330823998d.jpg&h=576bcb85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180408/640_18f5a6e3eac1f10c024d1b5e68234486.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180408%2F640_18f5a6e3eac1f10c024d1b5e68234486.jpg&h=76f42a01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180408/640_ef29591eee8d4653675f07c3ee71baf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180408%2F640_ef29591eee8d4653675f07c3ee71baf9.jpg&h=7bcd7147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7f54719d84e85652141de18e5fd49038feee65","tid":620933,"uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"